      "Text": "Security update for the Linux Kernel (Live Patch 2 for SLE 15 SP7)",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for the Linux Kernel 6.4.0-150700_53_6 fixes several issues.\n\nThe following security issues were fixed:\n\n- CVE-2025-38494: HID: core: do not bypass hid_hw_raw_request (bsc#1247350).\n- CVE-2025-38495: HID: core: ensure the allocated report buffer can contain the reserved report ID (bsc#1247351).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
